---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - HavenKeep">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
      <strong>Last Updated:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
    </p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          By accessing or using HavenKeep ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the Service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          HavenKeep is a warranty tracking application that helps you:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Track product warranties and expiration dates</li>
          <li>Store receipts and warranty documentation</li>
          <li>Receive reminders before warranties expire</li>
          <li>Manage items across multiple properties</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. User Accounts</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">3.1 Account Creation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          You must create an account to use the Service. You agree to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
          <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
          <li>Notify us immediately of unauthorized use</li>
          <li>Be responsible for all activity under your account</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">3.2 Account Termination</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We may suspend or terminate your account if you:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Violate these Terms</li>
          <li>Engage in fraudulent activity</li>
          <li>Abuse or misuse the Service</li>
          <li>Fail to pay subscription fees</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Subscription and Payments</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.1 Free Plan</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Up to 10 items</li>
          <li>Basic warranty tracking</li>
          <li>Email reminders</li>
          <li>No credit card required</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.2 Premium Plan ($4.99/month)</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Unlimited items</li>
          <li>Barcode scanning</li>
          <li>Receipt OCR (optical character recognition)</li>
          <li>PDF export</li>
          <li>Priority support</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.3 Billing</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Subscriptions are billed monthly in advance</li>
          <li>Automatic renewal unless canceled</li>
          <li>Price changes will be communicated 30 days in advance</li>
          <li>Payments processed securely through Stripe</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4.4 Refunds</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We offer a 14-day money-back guarantee for first-time Premium subscribers. After 14 days, subscriptions are non-refundable. You may cancel at any time to prevent future charges.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. User Content</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">5.1 Your Data</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          You retain ownership of all data you upload (item information, receipts, photos). By using the Service, you grant us a license to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Store and process your data to provide the Service</li>
          <li>Use anonymized, aggregated data for analytics and improvements</li>
          <li>Display your data back to you across devices</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">5.2 Prohibited Content</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">You may not upload:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Illegal or harmful content</li>
          <li>Content that violates others' rights</li>
          <li>Malware or malicious code</li>
          <li>Excessive or spam content</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">You agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Reverse engineer or attempt to extract source code</li>
          <li>Use automated scripts or bots to access the Service</li>
          <li>Attempt to bypass security measures</li>
          <li>Interfere with other users' access</li>
          <li>Use the Service for illegal purposes</li>
          <li>Resell or redistribute the Service</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The Service, including its design, features, and content (excluding your user content), is owned by HavenKeep and protected by copyright, trademark, and other laws. You may not copy, modify, or distribute our intellectual property without permission.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Disclaimers and Limitations</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">8.1 Service Availability</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The Service is provided "as is" without warranties. We do not guarantee:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Uninterrupted or error-free operation</li>
          <li>100% uptime (we target 99.9%)</li>
          <li>Data accuracy from barcode/OCR scanning</li>
          <li>Warranty validity or coverage details</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">8.2 Limitation of Liability</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, HavenKeep is not liable for:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Indirect, incidental, or consequential damages</li>
          <li>Loss of data or profits</li>
          <li>Missed warranty deadlines</li>
          <li>Third-party warranty claim denials</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Our total liability is limited to the amount you paid us in the 12 months preceding the claim.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">8.3 Warranty Information</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          HavenKeep is a tracking tool only. We do not:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Provide warranty services or repairs</li>
          <li>Guarantee warranty coverage or claim approval</li>
          <li>Offer legal advice about warranty rights</li>
          <li>Verify manufacturer warranty terms</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Always verify warranty details with the manufacturer or retailer.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The Service integrates with third-party services (barcode databases, OCR providers). We are not responsible for their availability, accuracy, or terms of service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">10. Indemnification</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          You agree to indemnify and hold HavenKeep harmless from any claims arising from:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Your use of the Service</li>
          <li>Your violation of these Terms</li>
          <li>Your violation of others' rights</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">11. Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          These Terms are governed by the laws of [Your Jurisdiction], without regard to conflict of law provisions. Any disputes will be resolved in the courts of [Your Jurisdiction].
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We may update these Terms from time to time. Significant changes will be communicated via email or in-app notification 30 days in advance. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">13. Severability</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          If any provision of these Terms is found to be invalid, the remaining provisions will remain in full effect.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">14. Contact Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          For questions about these Terms, contact us at:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-none text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@havenkeep.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">legal@havenkeep.com</a></li>
          <li><strong>Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@havenkeep.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">support@havenkeep.com</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
      <a href="/" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .prose h3 {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
